    {
      "id": "task-graph-summary-overview",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Task Summary",
      "position": {
        "x": -460,
        "y": -220
      },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Task Summary\n\nA node view exposes a summary.\n\nFor **task graphs**, the summary should tell the host graph what matters immediately:\n\n- the goal\n- the status\n- `x/y` tasks completed\n- `x/y` questions answered",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
